data.current_description: Notifies that a URL has been updated or deleted.
data.summary_suggestion: Notify Google Search of URL updates or deletions
data.description_suggestion: Publishes a notification to Google Web Search about a URL change event. Accepts a UrlNotification object specifying the URL and notification type (UPDATE or DELETE). This operation informs Google's indexing system that a web page has been updated or removed, triggering a re-crawl or removal from the search index. Returns a PublishUrlNotificationResponse confirming successful receipt. Requires OAuth 2.0 authentication.
